PN,41201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776985387
OL,3,CWilliam tries out replica race car and
OL,4,Cjokes about AI drivers at Formula E
OL,5,Cbase
OL,7,FThe Prince of Wales has tried out a
OL,8,F"fantastic" replica of a Jaguar
OL,9,FFormula E (FE) racing car, as he joked
OL,10,Fabout drivers being replaced by
OL,11,Fartificial intelligence (AI).
OL,13,FWilliam met drivers and engineers at
OL,14,FJaguar TCS Racing's base in Kidlington
OL,15,Fin Oxfordshire, working on new
OL,16,Ftechnologies in the world's fastest-
OL,17,Fgrowing electric motorsport.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@KO]
