OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776985387
OL,3,CWilliam tries out replica race car and
OL,4,Cjokes about AI drivers at Formula E
OL,5,Cbase
OL,7,FIn the factory, the prince was greeted
OL,8,Fby Antonio Felix da Costa, the 2020 FE
OL,9,Fworld champion, who offered him the
OL,10,Fchance to sit behind the wheel of a
OL,11,Fdevelopment car, identical to the
OL,12,Fteam's current model.
OL,14,F"There's not a lot of room in the
OL,15,Flegs, is there?" joked William, who
OL,16,Fstands at 6ft 3in, as he settled into
OL,17,Fthe car.
OL,19,FDa Costa talked the prince through
OL,20,Fwhat it is like to race the car, as
OL,21,Fwell as its equipment and features.
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@PO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776985387
OL,3,CWilliam tries out replica race car and
OL,4,Cjokes about AI drivers at Formula E
OL,5,Cbase
OL,7,F"And your head, would you be slightly
OL,8,Flower down?" William asked.
OL,10,F"I would say slightly lower than you
OL,11,Fare now," Da Costa replied.
OL,13,FBefore getting out of the car, the
OL,14,Fprince thanked the sportsman, adding
OL,15,F"that's fantastic".
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@LO]rD@AOUsD@IO]wD@AOUwD@RO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776985387
OL,3,CWilliam tries out replica race car and
OL,4,Cjokes about AI drivers at Formula E
OL,5,Cbase
OL,7,FWilliam, who is known to have an
OL,8,Finterest in the environment, appeared
OL,9,Fenthusiastic and engaged as he asked
OL,10,Fquestions about the sustainability
OL,11,Faspect of FE, something he described
OL,12,Fas "incredible", and told engineers
OL,13,Fthey are "doing very well".
OL,15,FHe wished the team luck ahead of their
OL,16,Fraces in Berlin next month, and said:
OL,17,F"I'm very excited to see you racing,
OL,18,FI'm going to cheer you guys on."
OL,26,@tD@DOUtD@OO]uD@JOUuD@ZO]yD@AOUzD@`O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776985387
OL,3,CWilliam tries out replica race car and
OL,4,Cjokes about AI drivers at Formula E
OL,5,Cbase
OL,7,FMeeting young engineers who had
OL,8,Fcompleted a graduate programme with
OL,9,FJaguar TCS Racing, the prince told
OL,10,Fthem he had joked with their
OL,11,Fcolleagues earlier that, with so many
OL,12,Finnovations in the sport, "at what
OL,13,Fpoint does the driver become the weak
OL,14,Flink?"
OL,16,FHe added: "(At what point do we think)
OL,17,Fget rid of drivers, we'll get an AI
OL,18,Fperson in?... We're probably not far
OL,19,Foff that, are we?"
OL,26,@tD@[OUvD@FO]xD@KOU{D@RO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776985387
OL,3,CWilliam tries out replica race car and
OL,4,Cjokes about AI drivers at Formula E
OL,5,Cbase
OL,7,FSpeaking to 22-year-old graduate
OL,8,FPhoebe Russell, the prince remarked
OL,9,Fthat motorsport is "not necessarily
OL,10,Fthe first thing women would think
OL,11,Fabout joining", asking: "Was it easy
OL,12,Ffor you to find your way into this
OL,13,Fworld?", to which she replied "not at
OL,14,Fall", adding that she had exposure to
OL,15,Fthe sport as a child.
OL,17,FSpeaking after the visit, Ms Russell
OL,18,Fsaid she was "in shock" after meeting
OL,19,Fthe prince.
OL,26,@qD@TOUsD@NO]sD@YOUuD@GO]uD@_OUvD@DO]zD@
OL,26,ANOUzD@WO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
