OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776985387
OL,3,CWilliam tries out replica race car and
OL,4,Cjokes about AI drivers at Formula E
OL,5,Cbase
OL,7,FShe said: "Being asked to do a little
OL,8,Fcareer talk was very exciting.
OL,10,F"The fact that he (William) had so
OL,11,Fmuch awareness of the sport and so
OL,12,Fmuch interest, and it ties into his
OL,13,Fwhole sustainability project, it was
OL,14,Fvery interesting."
OL,16,FJack Lambert, head of technical
OL,17,Fintegration at Jaguar TCS Racing, who
OL,18,Fgave the prince a tour of the
OL,19,Fpremises, joked that William's height
OL,20,Fcould make racing in the car
OL,21,Funcomfortable.
OL,26,@oD@KOUvD@RO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776985387
OL,3,CWilliam tries out replica race car and
OL,4,Cjokes about AI drivers at Formula E
OL,5,Cbase
OL,7,FMr Lambert said: "It's great to see
OL,8,Fhim in there, and that he was keen to
OL,9,Fget in it, because it's not an easy
OL,10,Fthing to get in and out of by any
OL,11,Fmeans.
OL,13,F"So for him to be so open to doing
OL,14,Fthat with everyone around, it's not a
OL,15,Fsmall ask, but he was really keen.
OL,17,F"And his interaction with Antonio, and
OL,18,FAntonio being able to tell him about
OL,19,Fhis world while he's behind the
OL,20,Fsteering wheel, it's awesome."
OL,26,@oD@ROUyD@AOU|D@^O]
